Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:38.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:39.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:41.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Para-sama's pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,To put me with Alti at this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:48.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are plenty of people for Paraietta to fly with,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:52.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,but you only have one sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:57.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ri Maajons you two draw together will certainly reflect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because we're sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:03.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is all for the sake of regaining Chor Tempest's honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:07.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,From now on, no more disgraceful conduct will be permitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:17.95,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:19.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:23.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you picking out all of your onions?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:26.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:30.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun, I didn't know you could be so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:34.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I guess it wasn't anything special, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:34.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:39.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were all "Oh, I'm in love!", and look at you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:42.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Mastif, you're so sweet.\N— What about killing people, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:49.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't take it out on me just because your beloved Para-sama dumped you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:52.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:12.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:23.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ah! Back to normal at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:27.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm so proud of you for putting up with all the inhuman things they did to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,You guys are awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:32.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas, I can't pretend I didn't hear you say "inhuman."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now there's a rare sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:55.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:03.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san didn't say that just to be mean to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:04.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:10.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, she's got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:16.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,My chest was going all "waaah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought my heart would stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:21.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:26.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:29.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:38.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't ever want to forget what happened that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:42.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:44.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,what happened that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:46.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:03.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Floe, more to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are we leaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:10.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun sibyllae, the {\i1}Messis{\i0} is honoured that you're helping us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:13.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable! How can this thing fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:14.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,My deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where's Kaimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:20.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still sulking. What a sourpuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:26.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:33.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaimu, Aaeru and I will be coming with you on tomorrow's patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:38.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, don't you care at all? We're not going to be a pair any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:40.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Settle down, Kaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, you haven't done anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:50.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I haven't done anything wrong, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:53.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:06:00.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's terribly confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:03.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I should go with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Uh oh! She broke it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:27.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yikes, that's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:31.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be all right when the rust was gone, but now this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:33.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,It won't come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:48.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I wash and wash,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,it won't come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:09.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's just go to sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:12.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, you must be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can come and sleep in my bed if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nope. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:20.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself. You're still little, so—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:22.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one who's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,I... I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:01.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:59.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the first time that we've flown together, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:01.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're just "praying to the sky."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:07.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,How did we get like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:11.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I mean, we used to be together all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,It must be because of that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:19.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,After them, Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:42.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru! The speaker cable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:49.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:52.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaimu! Alti!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:01.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why is their prayer having no effect on the Simoun Gem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they go into the clouds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:12.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we'll lose sight of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:18.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:21.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do {\i1}not{\i0} call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:33.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everything really {\i1}is{\i0} your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:41.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Alti, you're the one who screwed everything up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:45.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:47.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was {\i1}all{\i0} your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:46.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Eh? She's just as beat-up as the {\i1}Messis{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,But what is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:52.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's an Argentine logistical base ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:57.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I had no idea that they could make them so large!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:02.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're awfully close, but it doesn't look like they've spotted us yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:04.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wanna go have a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:06.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,No. It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,And there's something wrong with one of our Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:10.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,We should go back to the {\i1}Messis{\i0} and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,This was ridiculous from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:14.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even Dominura should understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:16.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just because we're sisters...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I... will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:26.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Alti?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:30.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san and I... we can make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want Dominura to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:39.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru and Kaimu will wait with the Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:42.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll approach cautiously and get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,If anything happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:46.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:25.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:37.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,A broken searchlight, and no guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:40.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,People like this are causing us so much pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:47.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're using {\i1}this{\i0} to go up against the chariots of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:51.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it matter to them that they're outmatched?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:53.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aren't they afraid of dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:57.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's anyone who doesn't fear death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,So. They're strong, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:02.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I envy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Alti.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:15.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't need to be strong by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:18.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's her fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:21.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's always...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:23.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's always getting in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:25.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why does she...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:31.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened between you and Alti?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:36.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,You two are weird. I mean, you're sisters, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:39.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}because{\i0} we're sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:42.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,That night...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:55.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,That night, I was weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:58.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,When morning came, it was going to be my first battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:00.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:03.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted to cry out, to run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:06.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:13.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that she came on to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:18.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,I couldn't resist what Alti was offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I dunno, I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:30.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course not. Between sisters, it's an abominable sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:36.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,In things like that, it's hard to say who's right and who's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't tell just from hearing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe you were the one who led her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:48.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Led her on? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:15.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have to make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get Alti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kaimu! Kaimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:31.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,When we were little, I was always crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:37.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,But every time, Nee-san would hold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I felt stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:54.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not that night that I want to get back to,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:56.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's those warm afternoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:03.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I want are not the hands that gave me sensations I'd never felt before,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:08.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,but rather the gentle hand that held mine as we walked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:13.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,But Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:17.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Someday I'll become a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:24.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then it will be my turn to hold Nee-san in my arms, as tightly as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:32.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:06.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san! Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:13.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san! What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:17.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you'll land in my arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:27.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:33.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not... my... fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:55.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaimu, when we get there, go straight to Aaeru's sagitta seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:56.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaimu! Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:58.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:37.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Their prayer had no effect on the Simoun Gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:42.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see. And something like this, you've...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,...never heard of before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:50.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Argentine base ship—we can't just leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:54.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,They had a new class of fighter based there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:05.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,To get stronger through someone else's embrace...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not the right way, Alti.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:15.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Only when both of you are strong can you really embrace each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:20.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, how's Nee-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:22.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just some scrapes and scratches.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:24.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:34.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't you and Amuria ever embrace each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:38.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right... if you do that with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.71,0:21:47.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,The reflection in your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:52.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is an image of yourself, never growing older.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:56.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.19,0:22:34.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,It tastes just like hers.
